1
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:41,240
♪In rain or shine♪

2
00:00:41,780 --> 00:00:46,870
♪When you're around,
the sun shines through♪

3
00:00:47,220 --> 00:00:52,640
♪Spare ourselves the endless thoughts
and guessing games♪

4
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:58,880
♪Let's just meet
and escape these frames♪

5
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:02,600
♪I stand within the shadows deep♪

6
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:08,030
♪My hand outstretched,
your rescue I keep♪

7
00:01:08,220 --> 00:01:12,850
♪Even if the world falls apart♪

8
00:01:13,170 --> 00:01:15,870
♪No distance is too far♪

9
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:21,390
♪To stop us from coming together♪

10
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:27,710
♪Through the night,
you're at the end of the line♪

11
00:01:28,710 --> 00:01:32,730
♪To protect you is my humble wish♪

12
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:36,920
♪Farewell, to the timid soul I knew♪

13
00:01:37,270 --> 00:01:42,550
♪It was you who made me brave and new♪

14
00:01:42,550 --> 00:01:46,180
=Always Home=
(Adapted from Xiao Ge's novel, Always Home)

15
00:01:46,260 --> 00:01:49,180
=Episode 4=
(Run! Speed: 140 miles per hour!)

16
00:01:54,370 --> 00:01:56,080
(No one would believe me.)

17
00:01:56,700 --> 00:01:58,690
(I always say I'm a soccer lover,)

18
00:01:58,930 --> 00:02:00,210
(and I seem fearless.)

19
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:02,440
(But if it weren't for my dad,)

20
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:06,920
(I would have given up
when I got injured before the recruitment.)

21
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:11,570
Coach.

22
00:02:11,890 --> 00:02:13,210
I know you mean well.

23
00:02:13,770 --> 00:02:14,640
However,

24
00:02:14,730 --> 00:02:16,419
I won't let Xichi

25
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:17,680
play soccer.

26
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:20,139
Let alone attend a soccer academy.

27
00:02:20,140 --> 00:02:21,569
He's trained

28
00:02:21,570 --> 00:02:22,960
so hard for years.

29
00:02:23,450 --> 00:02:25,640
You should let him see it through.

30
00:02:46,940 --> 00:02:48,640
(He reignited my motivation,)

31
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:51,050
(and convinced my mom
to let me continue playing.)

32
00:02:51,570 --> 00:02:52,329
(Of course,)

33
00:02:52,330 --> 00:02:54,360
(only if I don't get hurt again.)

34
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:17,960
Dad.

35
00:03:18,450 --> 00:03:19,609
You're really getting old.

36
00:03:19,610 --> 00:03:20,840
You couldn't keep up earlier.

37
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:22,920
I was literally feeding you marks earlier.

38
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:24,240
Watch your words.

39
00:03:33,610 --> 00:03:34,400
Xichi.

40
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:36,360
Promise me.

41
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:38,640
You can play soccer,

42
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,049
but remember,

43
00:03:40,050 --> 00:03:41,520
you promised Mom.

44
00:03:41,700 --> 00:03:43,170
If you get injured again,

45
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:45,010
you won't be able to play anymore.

46
00:03:45,290 --> 00:03:46,080
Got it.

47
00:03:46,770 --> 00:03:47,520
But dad.

48
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:49,539
We need

49
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:50,680
to go home now.

50
00:03:50,820 --> 00:03:52,379
Mom will be back soon.

51
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:53,859
I'll get going first.

52
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:56,960
Boy. I'm afraid of getting
caught by your mom too!

53
00:04:02,170 --> 00:04:02,840
Dad.

54
00:04:03,570 --> 00:04:05,240
Stay alert.

55
00:04:05,490 --> 00:04:07,139
Mom could be back any time now.

56
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:08,640
Don't you spill the beans.

57
00:04:14,890 --> 00:04:16,049
What are you doing?

58
00:04:16,050 --> 00:04:17,129
We've been home all day.

59
00:04:17,130 --> 00:04:18,520
How would our house look so clean?

60
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:20,770
You're sneaky indeed.

61
00:04:20,810 --> 00:04:21,770
Let's watch the match.

62
00:04:23,130 --> 00:04:24,570
It's starting.

63
00:04:39,100 --> 00:04:40,369
What's wrong with you two?

64
00:04:40,370 --> 00:04:43,199
Did you really have to turn the house
upside down just to watch a match?

65
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:45,400
You're so difficult.

66
00:04:48,610 --> 00:04:49,600
What's that smell?

67
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:52,520
Yunnan Baiyao.

68
00:04:53,050 --> 00:04:54,019
Xichi.

69
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,080
Did you play...

70
00:04:56,980 --> 00:04:57,779
Ouch!

71
00:04:57,780 --> 00:04:59,520
I need to spray this later.

72
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:03,489
Jing.

73
00:05:03,490 --> 00:05:05,459
If you're not feeling well,
just go see Song.

74
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,339
Yes, exactly.

75
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:07,840
What if you hurt your bones?

76
00:05:07,930 --> 00:05:08,809
Yes.

77
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:09,459
Okay.

78
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:10,289
Okay.

79
00:05:10,290 --> 00:05:12,729
I heard you have
sports day coming up.

80
00:05:12,730 --> 00:05:13,489
You better

81
00:05:13,490 --> 00:05:14,890
not register for anything.

82
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:18,210
But Mom.

83
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:20,049
Please.

84
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:20,779
Please, Mom.

85
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:22,010
Please, I beg you.

86
00:05:22,130 --> 00:05:23,609
My legs are perfectly fine.

87
00:05:23,610 --> 00:05:24,840
That's final.

88
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:25,929
Mom.

89
00:05:25,930 --> 00:05:27,689
Please let me go.

90
00:05:27,690 --> 00:05:29,289
I'm the class sports representative.

91
00:05:29,290 --> 00:05:31,019
I have to set an example.

92
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:33,249
Just get your classmates to join.

93
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:34,099
I will

94
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:35,579
talk to your teacher.

95
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:36,520
Mom.

96
00:05:36,610 --> 00:05:38,369
This affects our class performance.

97
00:05:38,370 --> 00:05:39,689
I have to compete.

98
00:05:39,690 --> 00:05:41,810
I'm the best in class at sports.

99
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:43,770
What about your leg?

100
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:46,419
It was injured.

101
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:47,339
It may have healed,

102
00:05:47,340 --> 00:05:48,129
but your knees

103
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:49,129
are still weak.

104
00:05:49,130 --> 00:05:50,010
Do you understand?

105
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:51,729
Don't worry, Mom.

106
00:05:51,730 --> 00:05:53,539
I know how to take care of myself.

107
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,219
I can still run.

108
00:05:55,220 --> 00:05:56,459
How can I not worry?

109
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:58,840
Song said

110
00:05:59,130 --> 00:06:01,169
you need to rest
and avoid strenuous activity.

111
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:02,400
Did you hear me?

112
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:03,570
Mom.

113
00:06:03,810 --> 00:06:05,489
Please, I beg you.

114
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:06,770
Beg?

115
00:06:06,810 --> 00:06:07,979
What a coward.

116
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:09,160
Mom!

117
00:06:09,810 --> 00:06:11,459
Our class has no other athletes.

118
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:13,659
If I don't compete,
we have no chance of winning.

119
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:16,419
Besides, I'm terrible at academics.
I've always dragged the class down.

120
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,289
This is my chance

121
00:06:17,290 --> 00:06:18,979
to contribute.

122
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:21,520
I don't want to be the laughing stock
of the other classes.

123
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:23,459
Jing Xichi.

124
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:25,219
Stop arguing with me.

125
00:06:25,220 --> 00:06:26,019
Save your energy

126
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,249
for studying.

127
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:28,659
Then you won't be a disappointment.

128
00:06:28,660 --> 00:06:29,600
Gosh.

129
00:06:30,690 --> 00:06:31,659
Go study.

130
00:06:31,660 --> 00:06:33,010
Mom.

131
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:34,690
Let me compete.

132
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:03,690
(I'll join.)

133
00:07:07,490 --> 00:07:08,480
Chen Huan'er!

134
00:07:08,690 --> 00:07:09,729
Are you serious?

135
00:07:09,730 --> 00:07:10,609
I'm very weak now.

136
00:07:10,610 --> 00:07:11,890
Don't lie to me.

137
00:07:13,490 --> 00:07:14,450
I'm serious.

138
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:18,370
You're the best!

139
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:21,600
I'll join regardless.

140
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:46,690
Are you hungry?

141
00:07:46,730 --> 00:07:47,930
Here, have some.

142
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:50,249
I made it myself.
I learned the recipe from Aunt Hao.

143
00:07:50,250 --> 00:07:51,369
You cooked this?

144
00:07:51,370 --> 00:07:52,840
That's right. Open up.

145
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:55,040
How is it?

146
00:07:59,130 --> 00:08:00,040
Not bad.

147
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:02,570
Didn't you say you don't like it?

148
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:04,960
I never said that.

149
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:06,019
I ate everything

150
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:07,129
you rejected.

151
00:08:07,130 --> 00:08:08,960
I think the vegetable
dumplings are good.

152
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:10,770
Listen.

153
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:12,369
My mom wasn't
thinking straight yesterday.

154
00:08:12,370 --> 00:08:13,960
She won't let me compete.

155
00:08:13,980 --> 00:08:15,040
Thank goodness you agreed.

156
00:08:15,490 --> 00:08:16,289
However,

157
00:08:16,290 --> 00:08:17,890
why'd you change your mind?

158
00:08:18,690 --> 00:08:20,330
That's none of your business.

159
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:21,979
Don't try to figure out

160
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:23,160
a girl's thought.

161
00:08:25,930 --> 00:08:26,720
By the way,

162
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:29,080
please don't tell my mom

163
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:30,489
that I'm competing.

164
00:08:30,490 --> 00:08:31,689
Don't snitch on me.

165
00:08:31,690 --> 00:08:33,120
Why all the secrecy?

166
00:08:34,490 --> 00:08:35,369
I told you.

167
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:37,450
Stop guessing my thoughts.

168
00:08:38,130 --> 00:08:39,000
Fine.

169
00:08:39,100 --> 00:08:40,840
I won't say anything.

170
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:42,099
We need to start

171
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:43,760
intensive training now.

172
00:08:44,130 --> 00:08:44,930
Okay.

173
00:08:47,730 --> 00:08:48,810
Are you that happy?

174
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:51,120
Our class has a secret weapon.

175
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:01,690
Hurry, we're almost there.

176
00:09:02,300 --> 00:09:03,889
I don't want to run anymore.

177
00:09:03,890 --> 00:09:06,409
- I can't keep going.
- You can't stop abruptly after the run.

178
00:09:06,410 --> 00:09:06,769
Come on.

179
00:09:06,770 --> 00:09:08,099
Walk slowly.

180
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,360
Let's walk slowly.

181
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:12,530
Song Cong.

182
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:15,579
I'm joining the 800m race.

183
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,819
Help me train.

184
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:18,179
You've competed

185
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:19,880
since junior middle school.

186
00:09:19,890 --> 00:09:21,570
Are you joining this round too?

187
00:09:21,610 --> 00:09:22,840
Not this time.

188
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:24,880
I'm the announcer.

189
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:28,000
Ask Xichi to train you then.

190
00:09:28,060 --> 00:09:29,120
He's a professional.

191
00:09:31,890 --> 00:09:32,579
Never mind then.

192
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:33,410
Goodbye.

193
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:37,249
Speed up.

194
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:38,219
Chen Huan'er.

195
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:40,249
This is your favorite orange.

196
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:42,889
- What are you doing?
- You can eat it at the finish line.

197
00:09:42,890 --> 00:09:44,649
Secret weapon? Her?

198
00:09:44,650 --> 00:09:45,979
Don't push her too hard.

199
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:49,179
She's just like you. You're still an amateur
even if you're the soccer team leader.

200
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:50,979
And you're no leader.

201
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:52,290
You're just a ball boy.

202
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:54,129
Ignore him. Focus on running.

203
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:54,859
Let it go.

204
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:56,880
- You can eat this when you finish.
- Put it down!

205
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:10,080
Come on, Chen Huan'er!

206
00:10:10,180 --> 00:10:11,410
Almost there!

207
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:18,409
