208
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:19,290
Are you okay?

209
00:10:19,580 --> 00:10:20,450
How is it?

210
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:21,699
As long as you finish.

211
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:23,000
Why are you so worked up?

212
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:26,960
I want to challenge myself.

213
00:10:28,250 --> 00:10:29,859
Regulate your breathing. Come on.

214
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:30,810
Drink some water.

215
00:10:32,410 --> 00:10:33,570
Drink slowly.

216
00:10:34,820 --> 00:10:35,760
Slowly.

217
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:44,769
I'm home.

218
00:10:44,770 --> 00:10:46,050
You're back.

219
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:49,880
Why are you late today?

220
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:53,489
What happened to your face?

221
00:10:53,490 --> 00:10:55,240
Why is your hair tangled?

222
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:58,459
I was on duty today.

223
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,050
I was sweating buckets.

224
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:01,059
Duty?

225
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:02,409
