228
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:08,160
- You shouldn't be doing manual labor.
- Okay. Don't worry, Mom.

229
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,930
I'm in top condition.

230
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,409
Nonsense.

231
00:11:11,410 --> 00:11:12,099
