232
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:13,579
After your Sports Day,

233
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:15,409
come to my workplace for lunch.

234
00:11:15,410 --> 00:11:16,530
Don't go home for food.

235
00:11:17,340 --> 00:11:18,760
